Claws-mail should not display a popup dialog when a message is being sent (one cannot use claws anymore until the message is sent).

Adding `send_dialog_mode=1` to clawsrc seems to do the trick.

Let's [[!taglink todo/test]] by changing this setting in
`~/.claws-mail/clawsrc` in a pristine Tails *before* running Claws.

